data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Kapolei! This delightful 3 bed, 2 bath home features an open floor plan that sets the stage for relaxation and social gatherings. Modern appliances adorn the stylish kitchen, ensuring meal preparation is a joy. Nestled within proximity to shopping and restaurants, convenience is at your fingertips. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this wonderful place in beautiful Hawaii your home!  Open House 4/14 from 2-5pm.
